Constance Shulman https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Constance_Shulman 0 Constance Shulman (born April 4, 1958) is an American actress. She is best known for voicing Patti Mayonnaise on Doug and for her current role as Yoga Jones in Orange Is the New Black. Shulman originated the role of Annelle in the first production of Steel Magnolias Off-Broadway. Constance_Shulman ( born April_4_,_1958 ) is an_American_actress .
